room_title: Escape room "ELF" by Central Arkansas Escape Rooms in Little Rock
room_address: 108 West F Avenue North Little Rock, AR 72116
room_description: It's Christmas time at Central Arkansas Escape Rooms! But wait ... Santa's elves are on strike! The sleigh won't fly, and orders are mixed up! Christmas may have to be cancelled, unless ... YOU assemble your own team of elves. Find the secret entrance to Santa's Workshop and GET. TO. WORK! Can you save Christmas!? There's only one way to find out!
